&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;code-block-indented-with-four-spaces&#34;&gt;Code block indented with four spaces&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;!doctype html&amp;gt;
